When using the Dopomoha.ro platform, as a user, you have several rights related to your personal data protection. According to Law no. 679/2016 and the General Data Protection Regulation, starting from May 25, 2018, these include:

* The right to be informed about how your personal data is processed on the platform;
* The right to access your personal data upon request and once per year at no cost;
* The right to intervene, correct, delete, or transfer your personal data upon request and without charge;
* The right to complain to the National Supervisory Authority for the Processing of Personal Data (www.dataprotection.ro) or file a lawsuit if necessary, to defend your legal rights;
* Starting from May 25, 2018, the right to object to automated individual decision-making processes involving your personal data, and
* The right to restrict the way your personal data is processed under specific circumstances.

